Two small utilities, which makes it possible to switch ambient light sensors on or off.
Also desktop notififactions are supported.

Works on Notebooks like
- HP EliteBook 8560p
- maybe others...

Dependencies:
- EFL (Eldbus, Ecore, Eeze, Eet, Eina)

Requires (for desktop notifications only):
- notification-daemon

Build & Install:
$ mkdir build
$ cd build/
$ cmake ..
$ make
$ make install

or on Archlinux:
$ cd packaging/
$ makepkg
$ pacman -U <pkgname>

Use:
$ hpals_client (to toggle ALS)